ğŸ§   Your Docker image size is very large. How do you reduce it?
    Use a smaller base image (e.g., alpine, distroless)
    Use multi-stage builds to keep only runtime files
    Remove unused packages, caches, and build tools
    Minimize layers and use .dockerignore
    Copy only required files into the image

