ğŸ§  Container is running but app is not reachable. What will you check?
Check container logs
docker logs <container_id>
Look for errors like port bind failed, DB not reachable, missing config
Sometimes the app starts but immediately fails to serve requests

Check the port inside container

Health/probes (if using Kubernetes)

If the container runs but app is unreachable:
Check app process, logs, port binding, host mapping, and network/firewall in that order.

